# What's the Hottest City?

## Overview

This Codecademy off-platform project focused on using Bash scripting to collect weather data for multiple cities, process the results, and present them in a sorted format. The project reinforced my understanding of variables, loops, command substitution, and text processing while providing additional practice with common Linux utilities.

